graphics:  make a house in day, then when clicked turn the sky to night

fizzbuzz-- 1 to 100, if divisible by 3 write fizz after it; if divisible by 5 write buzz

images-- blend two images together, make a collage, or andy warhol
effect of the same image in 4 different colors (colby college 
http://cs.colby.edu/courses/F11/cs151-labs/P05-BlendedCollages.php


new ideas:  plagiarism detection:  how much of two files match
turns into longest common substring, needs recursion and good
	explanation of dynamic programming.